Controversial media personality, Kemi Olunloyo has threatened to kill herself if Nigerians refuse to offer her financial help. Kemi took to her social media page to cry bitterly, while narrating how she has been passing through difficult times as a result of health crisis. According to her, she has asked that everyone donate a sum of two thousand Naira each for which she would be needing for Post-traumatic stress disorder (PTSD) therapy. However, she has threatened to kill herself if this is not done. Watch video below: Kemi Olunloyo threatens suicide if her fans don't donate N2,000 to her PTSD therapy A post shared by  DATSWASUP (@datswasup) on Jun 10, 2019 at 10:44pm PDT Source